data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-beds with SPACIOUS BONUS ROOM that could be a 4th bedroom.  Corner townhome in Canterbury Square. Boasting an elegant brick exterior and a spacious patio. The open layout seamlessly connects the living room and kitchen with tile flooring throughout the main living area. Generously-sized primary bedroom located on the main floor. The custom-built primary closet is sure to impress, offering ample storage and organizational space for all your wardrobe needs. The kitchen is equipped with double drawer Kitchen Aid dishwasher, perfect for handling large meals and dinner parties effortlessly. Upgraded plantation shutters throughout the home. Upstairs includes 2 bedrooms, one bath & expansive bonus room that is a versatile space that can be utilized as a 4th bedroom, play area, home office, or entertainment zone. Two-car garage and the practicality of a floored attic space provide ample room for storage. Floorplan available.
